title: Andorra end longest winless run in international football of EIGHTY-SIX games with 2-0 triumph away at San Marino who haven’t secured a victory since 2004
text:
EFL THE CINDERELLA DERBY Andorra end longest winless run in international football of EIGHTY-SIX games with 2-0 triumph away at San Marino who haven’t secured a victory since 2004 
It is only Andorra's fourth ever victory, with goalscorer Ildefons Lima describing how it is 'like winning a tournament' by JOHN HUTCHINSON
